                  </div>

                  <a href="portfolio" class="card__cta">See my projects -></a>
              </div>

              <div class="card">
                <div class="card__icons">
                  <a href="6ea42e9b2672806b1b63e2ae524346f6" class="card__icon">
                    <i class="fab fa-dribbble"></i>
                  </a>
                  <a href="af4151532dc3aff5002690c97346e069" class="card__icon">
                    <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                  </a>
                </div>

                <h3>Designer</h3>
                <p class="card__description">
                  I enjoy designing minimal interfaces for web and mobile apps. I'm sharing some of my work online.
                </p>

                <p class="card__description">On top of this, I also like to design <a class="underline " href="/wallpapers">wallpapers</a>.</p>
